>Descrizione del parametro <link linkend="cmd_menu_param_hotkey"
><parameter
>scorciatoia</parameter
></link
> del comando <command
>&no-i18n-cmd_menu;</command
>(). </para>
	</simplesect>
	</sect2>

	<!-- @COMMAND@ window:tile() -->
	<sect2 id="cmd_sect_window_tile"
><title id="cmd_title_window_tile"
>&no-i18n-cmd_window_tile;</title>
